Package: escluse-agent
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Escluse Team <team@escluse.com>
Description: Escluse Agent - Background service for managing game servers
 Escluse Agent connects your server to the Escluse platform, enabling
 game server management through a web control panel. Supports Minecraft
 (Java & Bedrock), Valheim, Palworld, and more.
